{"tid":352321,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2018DSE] 塵歸麈土歸土, 自修同儕再上路","createTime":"2017-08-08T16:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T06:13:39.000Z","uid":125535,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc22aea8af71165b0f751ece6c093a48aa84191","tid":352321,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T16:47:32.000Z","msg":"結果都塵埃落定, 決定左自修既巴打絲打入黎吹下水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8月8日之後, 大家有咩打算? 開始溫書未? 駛唔駛搵人幫手?<br />\n如果係同路人, 一齊過黎<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">圍爐取暖</span></strong>, 傾計交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴絲打仲煩緊應唔應該自修的話, 可以睇呢個POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/318130/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/318130/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你知道晒retake既利弊, 但未做到決定, 可以睇呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/317850/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/317850/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外, 自修同學會2018已經係7月成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎自修巴絲打加入WhatsApp群。8月份自修同學會有一次聚會, <span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>邀請左舊年既巴絲打分享佢地過一年既自修經歷同心得</strong></span>, 唔駛錢既。如果巴絲打有興趣加入同學會或者黎聚會, 就係下面條拎留低聯絡方法啦!<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/n9kjaX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fn9kjaX&d=7l2NxX2U2C0wnsvbV6UrZsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c946116e\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/n9kjaX</a>"},{"pid":"deb40df89ea052b6b55191c73ddd88c338b0767f","tid":352321,"uid":60261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f48e43bc1e95d7ad1eb194331294881f6edc73a","tid":352321,"uid":28489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"